      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a fantastic ride that strikes the perfect balance between quality and value? This car is in good condition and has been well-cared for, making it a reliable choice for your daily adventures! While it has been enjoyed on the road, it remains clean, dependable, and ready to hit the pavement with its next owner.",
