      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior retains a vibrant, high-gloss finish, showing only minor, expected signs of careful road use, while the wheels are clean and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is plush and free of tears, the carpets have been kept under protective mats, and the interior retains a fresh, neutral scent. Every button, dial, and digital display functions perfectly, from the ice-cold climate control to the premium audio system. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, reflecting a documented history of timely oil changes and preventative maintenance. This car offers a tight, responsive driving experience with confident braking and seamless gear shifts, making it a reliable and sophisticated choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
